graph LR
    P[Producer: Order Service] -- OrderCreated --> B[Message Broker: Kafka/RabbitMQ]
    
    B -- Subscribe --> C1[Consumer: Inventory Service]
    B -- Subscribe --> C2[Consumer: Email Service]
    B -- Subscribe --> C3[Consumer: Shipping Service]

    subgraph Error_Handling
        C1 -- Failed 3x --> DLQ[(Dead Letter Queue)]
        DLQ -- Manual Analysis --> Dev[Developer/Ops]
    end

    C1 --> DB1[(Inventory DB)]
    C2 --> SMTP[SMTP Server]
    C3 --> API[Logistics API]
